Jane the Junk Pirate

Occupation:
[] Junk Pirate (previously pirate)

Likes:
[] Fixing broken things, hoarding

Dislikes:
[] Throwing things away.

Favourite quote:
[] Ahoy there, matey!

Favourite people in the (living) world:
[] My grand daughter, my parrot Holly.

How I came to be here:
[] A fight with a shark that did not go well for me.

What I wish:
[] To go swimming with my grand daughter.
